==English==
===Etymology===
From [[trans-]] + [[action]]

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-transaction.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''transaction'''

# The act of [[conduct]]ing or [[carry]]ing out ([[business]], [[negotiation]]s, [[plan]]s).
# A [[deal]] or business [[agreement]].
# An [[exchange]] or [[trade]], as of ideas, money, goods, etc.
# (''in banking'') The [[transfer]] of [[fund]]s into, out of, or from an [[account]].
# A [[database transaction]].

